text: Henk Hulzebos (born 11 April 1950) is an Austrian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Austria Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Drenthe
